OL,3,CGovernment to publish nationalities of
OL,4,Cforeign criminals for first time
OL,6,FA Home Office source said: "Not only
OL,7,Fare we deporting foreign criminals at
OL,8,Fa rate never seen when Chris Philp and
OL,9,FRobert Jenrick were in charge at the
OL,10,FHome Office, but we will also be
OL,11,Fpublishing far more information about
OL,12,Fthat cohort of offenders than the
OL,13,FTories ever did."
OL,15,FThe latest data shows there were
OL,16,F19,244 foreign offenders awaiting
OL,17,Fdeportation at the end of 2024, up
OL,18,Ffrom 17,907 when the Conservatives
OL,19,Fleft office in July and 14,640 at the
OL,20,Fend of 2022.
